summary.p: This is an unofficial version of the game, created by a fan, and has not been validated by the creator of Ticket to Ride, Alan R. Moon, or Days of Wonder. You need to buy at least one of the official base versions to play this map.
Based on the road network of West Dorset, this map was designed to accommodate a larger group of players than usual.

action.description: Draw four cards from the tickets draw pile. Keep at least one. Zero to three of the newly drawn cards may be discarded.
Draw up to two train cards (normal or wild) from the face-up river.

collection.name: Players tickets
collection.description: Tickets that the player is expected to complete.

collection.name: Players carriages
collection.description: Carriage tokens in the players colour (that haven't yet been used to claim anything).

collection.name: Players stations
collection.description: Station tokens in the players colour (that haven't yet been used to claim a location).

collection.name: Ticket discard pile
collection.description: Tickets that have been discarded by players.
